Class PublishedFileDetailsCallback

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.co.thomasc.steamkit.steam3.steamclient.callbackmgr.CallbackMsg

  • public final class PublishedFileDetailsCallback
extends CallbackMsg
    This callback is received in response to calling SteamWorkshop.requestPublishedFileDetails(long).
